    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "仕事なら仕方ない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 186.9333092846
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh013.wav",
              "text": "分かりました。仕事なら仕方ないですね",
              "startTime": 186.9333092846,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "嫌だ、デートしたい",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 191.4666426179
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh014.wav",
              "text": "嫌です。そう言ってもう何回デートの約束を\n破ったと思ってるんですか。俺は莉央さんと\n一緒に記念日を過ごしたいです",
              "startTime": 191.4666426179,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-rio015.wav",
              "text": "私だって同じ気持ちよ\nでも、私にはプロジェクトを任された\n責任があるの。分かるでしょ？",
              "startTime": 199.5333092846,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh015.wav",
              "text": "……そうですね。莉央さんは俺と違って\n責任ある立場ですもんね\nわがままを言ってすみませんでした",
              "startTime": 207.8666416006,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "瑠依に相談しない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 320.9333184398
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh022.wav",
              "text": "ありがとう、瑠依。でも、やめておくよ\nこれは俺の問題だから、俺が自分で考えて\n解決しないといけないんだ",
              "startTime": 320.9333184398,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-rui007.wav",
              "text": "それなら仕方ないけど……\n相談したくなったら\n遠慮しないでいつでも声を掛けて――",
              "startTime": 330.2666497386,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 6800.000000000011
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 336.3666499293
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-suzuki001.wav",
              "text": "あれ？　お前達、こんな所に二人きりで\n何してるんだ？　あ、もしかして……\n二人は内緒で付き合ってるのか！？",
              "startTime": 337.0666497386,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 344.100004069
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-rui011.wav",
              "text": "鈴木君！？\nいきなり現れて何を言い出すのよ",
              "startTime": 347.2999891754,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-suzuki003.wav",
              "text": "誤魔化さなくていいって\nそうじゃないかと前から思ってたんだ\n同期として俺は二人の熱愛を祝福するぜ！",
              "startTime": 351.3333286123,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "こりゃあ、俺も負けていられないな\nよーし、莉央さんに告白して\nお前達みたいにラブラブになってやるぜ！",
              "startTime": 360.8333448884,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 11633.291912400011
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh028.wav",
              "text": "俺と瑠依はそんな関係じゃ……\n……ん？　今、廊下の向こうで誰かが\nこっちを見ていたような……気のせいか？",
              "startTime": 370.7333333333,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "瑠依に相談する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "choice_selection",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "text": "予約したレストランに瑠依と行く",
                  "route": []
                },
                {
                  "text": "やっぱり瑠依に相談するのはやめる",
                  "route": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 382.4666822907
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh023.wav",
              "text": "ありがとう\nそれなら今夜、仕事終わりに\n二人きりで会って話せないかな？",
              "startTime": 382.4666822907,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-rui008.wav",
              "text": "構わないわよ\n帰りに食事でもしながら話しましょう",
              "startTime": 387.9333489574,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh024.wav",
              "text": "（食事か……。そう言えば\n今夜は莉央さんと記念日を祝うために\nレストランを予約しておいたんだよな）",
              "startTime": 392.200015624,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 399.6400154905
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.133333381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_06_01-koh001.wav",
      "text": "ただいま",
      "startTime": 1.9666667144,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 999.9996978999999
